snippet.title: The Terminator - PSP (Minis) 2010
snippet.description:
Running on ppsspp
a simple arcade like shooter
here you walk with lesft directionals 
and fire with action buttons like a cross compass
L and R to change weapons

#psp #terminator #playstationportable 
#retrogaming #rudolphmaia #revivalhorror
